menu_items.item_description: Tender chicken cooked with Ethiopian spices, barbecue sauce, onion, garlic, and gluten free bread injera.
Tender pieces of lamb braised in Ethiopian special barbecue sauce served with bread injera gluten free.
Yebeg siga wot(Mild spicy lamb), and yebeg alicha wot(None spicy lamb). Served with side of gluten free bread injera with chicken and beef.
Split lentil, split peas, shio, green beans, cabbage, carrot, potato, collared green.
